cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.CV

This paper deals with machine translation, which falls under the category of natural language processing (NLP). Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also proposes a solution using neural networks, which falls under the categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper uses simulated low-resource scenarios, which could fall under the category of neural networks (cs.NE) or computer vision (cs.CV) if image data is involved.
